data.description: Gorgeous home perfect for entertaining! REAL hardwood floors, BIG open den & fireplace.TWO story dining room windows add a touch of elegance. Kitchen has beautiful MAPLE GLAZED cabinets, eating area & LOTS of cabinet space. LARGE master bedroom & bathroom featuring a walk in closet, separate vanities, jetted garden tub & separate shower. THIS IS A SPLIT BEDROOM PLAN! 2 bedrooms & bathroom are on the other side of the house. Carry your party to the 12x16 deck w/ built in gas line for your grill, or the TOTALLY PAVED PATIO spanning nearly the width of the house below the deck! PLUS the daylight basement has 2 car parking, storage & 2 MORE future ROOMS framed and a FULL BATHROOM stubbed waiting to be finished. Have as many people over as you want, the poured driveway is EXTRA LARGE!! Large corner lot in Brookhaven Subdivision featuring a pool & clubhouse. Did I mention the backyard would be ideal for your own pool?! **Saved THE BEST 4 last:**SELLER'S CREDIT $8,000 TO BUYERS W/ FULL OFFER!
